<h6 id="step-2-organizing-content-with-divs-and-grid-classes"><strong>Step 2 - Organizing content with divs and grid classes</strong></h6>

<p>Based on Chloe’s designs, we want the main content of our pages to be centered and we want it to automatically adjust to an appropriate width on different screen sizes. Chloe would like the content to take up the <strong>full width</strong> of the page on xs devices (This is a default! Yay!), about <strong>two-thirds</strong> of the page on sm devices and <strong>half</strong> the page on md and lg devices. </p>

